   Mailing Lists

   Sign up for one or more of our electronic distribution lists. This will
   assure that you will receive the most up-to-date information on all of
   our programs. You can also unsubscribe (below). We do not make our
   lists available to third parties.

   Email: _________________________
      [ ]  SIM Newsletter - Mailing List 'sim-announce'
   This list is used for our e-mail SIM Newsletter, issued about every 2
   months, and occasionally for other announcements. We maintain a
   Newsletter Archive.

      [ ]   Michelson Fellowship Program
   Hear about upcoimg events such as the interferometry summer school,
   graduate student and postdoctoral fellowships and undergraduate
   research opportunities. Please look also at the fellowship home page.

