   Publications
   Taking the Measure of the Universe
   A comprehensive overview of all aspects of the Space Interferometry
   Program. Published in March 1999. To receive a free hardcopy of this
   140 page book send an email with your complete shipping address and the
   number of copies you are requesting to Debi Fambro
   (Debi.Fambro@jpl.nasa.gov).
   Alternatively, you can also download the book as a set of PDF files
   from this Web site.
